input: what is the body weight change of patient 006-161415 last measured on the first hospital visit compared to the second to last value measured on the first hospital visit?
predict:
WITH first_stay AS (
    SELECT *
    FROM patient
    WHERE uniquepid = '006-161415'
    ORDER BY hospitaladmittime ASC
    LIMIT 1
),
weights AS (
    SELECT 
        admissionweight AS weight,
        hospitaladmittime AS time,
        'admission' AS type
    FROM first_stay
    UNION ALL
    SELECT 
        dischargeweight AS weight,
        hospitaldischargetime AS time,
        'discharge' AS type
    FROM first_stay
),
valid_weights AS (
    SELECT * FROM weights WHERE weight IS NOT NULL
),
ordered_weights AS (
    SELECT
        weight,
        type,
        time,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY time ASC) AS rn
    FROM valid_weights
)
SELECT 
    (MAX(CASE WHEN rn = (SELECT MAX(rn) FROM ordered_weights) THEN weight END)
     - 
     MAX(CASE WHEN rn = (SELECT MAX(rn)-1 FROM ordered_weights) THEN weight END)
    ) AS weight_change

input: for patients diagnosed with chronic kidney disease, show me the five year survival rate.
predict:
WITH ckd_patients AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT p.patientunitstayid, p.hospitaldischargetime, p.hospitaldischargestatus
    FROM patient p
    JOIN diagnosis d ON p.patientunitstayid = d.patientunitstayid
    WHERE d.diagnosisname LIKE '%chronic kidney disease%'
),
ckd_with_5y AS (
    SELECT
        c.patientunitstayid,
        c.hospitaldischargetime,
        c.hospitaldischargestatus,
        MIN(p2.hospitaldischargetime) AS next_outcome_time,
        p2.hospitaldischargestatus AS status_in_5y
    FROM ckd_patients c
    LEFT JOIN patient p2
        ON c.patientunitstayid = p2.patientunitstayid
        AND p2.hospitaldischargetime > c.hospitaldischargetime
        AND p2.hospitaldischargetime <= datetime(c.hospitaldischargetime, '+5 years')
    GROUP BY c.patientunitstayid
),
outcome_status AS (
    SELECT
        c.patientunitstayid,
        CASE
            WHEN c.status_in_5y IS NULL AND (c.hospitaldischargetime IS NOT NULL)
                AND (julianday('2105-12-31 23:59:00') - julianday(c.hospitaldischargetime) >= 5*365)
                AND c.hospitaldischargestatus = 'alive'
                THEN 1
            WHEN c.status_in_5y = 'alive'
                THEN 1
            WHEN c.status_in_5y = 'expired'
                THEN 0
            WHEN c.status_in_5y IS NULL AND (c.hospitaldischargetime IS NOT NULL)
                AND (julianday('2105-12-31 23:59:00') - julianday(c.hospitaldischargetime) < 5*365)
                THEN NULL
            ELSE NULL
        END AS survived_5y
    FROM ckd_with_5y c
)
SELECT
    ROUND(100.0 * SUM(CASE WHEN survived_5y = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 1.0 / COUNT(survived_5y), 2) AS five_year_survival_rate_percent
FROM outcome_status
WHERE survived_5y IS NOT NULL;

FROM survival_status;

    COUNT(*) AS prescription_count
FROM
    diagnosis d
JOIN patient p ON d.patientunitstayid = p.patientunitstayid
JOIN medication m ON d.patientunitstayid = m.patientunitstayid
WHERE
    d.diagnosisname = 'hepatic dysfunction - severe'
    AND p.gender = 'female'
    AND p.age LIKE '4%'  -- age in 40s (e.g., '40', '41', ..., '49')
    AND d.diagnosistime BETWEEN '2104-12-31 23:59:00' AND '2105-12-31 23:59:00'
    AND m.drugstarttime >= d.diagnosistime
    AND m.drugstarttime < datetime(d.diagnosistime, '+2 months')
GROUP BY
    m.drugname
ORDER BY
    prescription_count DESC
LIMIT 4;
real: select t3.drugname from ( select t2.drugname, dense_rank() over ( order by count(*) desc ) as c1 from ( select patient.uniquepid, diagnosis.diagnosistime from diagnosis join patient on diagnosis.patientunitstayid = patient.patientunitstayid where diagnosis.diagnosisname = 'hepatic dysfunction - severe' and datetime(diagnosis.diagnosistime,'start of year') = datetime('2105-12-31 23:59:00','start of year','-1 year') ) as t1 join ( select patient.uniquepid, medication.drugname, medication.drugstarttime from medication join patient on medication.patientunitstayid = patient.patientunitstayid where patient.gender = 'female' and patient.age between 40 and 49 and datetime(medication.drugstarttime,'start of year') = datetime('2105-12-31 23:59:00','start of year','-1 year') ) as t2 on t1.uniquepid = t2.uniquepid where t1.diagnosistime < t2.drugstarttime and datetime(t2.drugstarttime) between datetime(t1.diagnosistime) and datetime(t1.diagnosistime,'+2 month') group by t2.drugname ) as t3 where t3.c1 <= 4;

  AND lab.labresulttime > diagnosis.diagnosistime
  AND lab.labresulttime <= patient.hospitaldischargetime
GROUP BY lab.labname
ORDER BY freq DESC
LIMIT 4;

LIMIT 5;

input: retrieve the top five most frequent lab tests that patients were given during the same month after receiving vasodilator for pulmonary hypertension the previous year.
predict:
WITH vasodilator_patients AS (
    SELECT
        m.patientunitstayid,
        strftime('%Y', m.drugstarttime) AS year_start,
        strftime('%m', m.drugstarttime) AS month_start
    FROM medication m
    WHERE
        m.drugname LIKE '%vasodilator%'
        AND EXISTS (
            SELECT 1
            FROM diagnosis d
            WHERE
                d.patientunitstayid = m.patientunitstayid
                AND d.diagnosisname LIKE '%pulmonary hypertension%'
                AND d.diagnosistime <= m.drugstarttime
        )
        AND m.drugstarttime IS NOT NULL
),
year_month_lab_patients AS (
    SELECT
        l.labname,
        l.patientunitstayid,
        vp.year_start AS event_year,
        vp.month_start AS event_month,
        strftime('%Y', l.labresulttime) AS lab_year,
        strftime('%m', l.labresulttime) AS lab_month
    FROM lab l
    JOIN vasodilator_patients vp
      ON l.patientunitstayid = vp.patientunitstayid
    WHERE
        -- lab is 1 year after vasodilator administration
        l.labresulttime >= datetime(vp.year_start || '-' || vp.month_start || '-01', '+1 year')
        AND l.labresulttime < datetime(vp.year_start || '-' || vp.month_start || '-01', '+1 year', '+1 month')
        -- lab is in the same month (but 1 year later) as vasodilator administration
        AND strftime('%m', l.labresulttime) = vp.month_start
        AND strftime('%Y', l.labresulttime) = (CAST(vp.year_start AS INTEGER) + 1)
)
SELECT
    labname,
    COUNT(*) AS freq
FROM year_month_lab_patients
GROUP BY labname
ORDER BY freq DESC
LIMIT 5;
real: select t3.labname from ( select t2.labname, dense_rank() over ( order by count(*) desc ) as c1 from ( select patient.uniquepid, treatment.treatmenttime from treatment join patient on treatment.patientunitstayid = patient.patientunitstayid where treatment.treatmentname = 'vasodilator for pulmonary hypertension' and datetime(treatment.treatmenttime,'start of year') = datetime('2105-12-31 23:59:00','start of year','-1 year') ) as t1 join ( select patient.uniquepid, lab.labname, lab.labresulttime from lab join patient on lab.patientunitstayid = patient.patientunitstayid where datetime(lab.labresulttime,'start of year') = datetime('2105-12-31 23:59:00','start of year','-1 year') ) as t2 on t1.uniquepid = t2.uniquepid where t1.treatmenttime < t2.labresulttime and datetime(t1.treatmenttime,'start of month') = datetime(t2.labresulttime,'start of month') group by t2.labname ) as t3 where t3.c1 <= 5;
